{"tid":2128270,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沉迷賭博，倒錢落海，各位記住，控制注碼","createTime":"2020-07-28T01:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T03:32:26.000Z","uid":102938,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa6d21ea6c0bb83ceab6d3ffd6419a90d6e90fd","tid":2128270,"uid":102938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:00:11.000Z","msg":"今次出post原因係自己又再次因為賭錢而倒錢落海<br />\n所以係到好想提醒各位，千萬唔好沉迷賭博<br />\n以我為例，近幾年賭錢夾夾埋埋肯定輸至少20萬起<br />\n但明明可以賺錢收手我就次次都忍唔住手<br />\n上個六月用1萬本金賺到上6萬幾，平均每注都係用一千幾百<br />\n但慢慢愈賺愈多結果就一萬幾千一注，結果連輸幾注玩完<br />\n好啦到今個七月用2萬本金賺到上4萬幾，結果同六月一樣<br />\n又係由平注慢慢磨到上去但亦係連續幾波一萬注就玩完<br />\n而係到要多謝幾位巴打：屎怪巴、曹操巴、Angus巴、不器巴<br />\n因為肯聽我呻真係已經好好，琴日明明仲有4萬幾之後連輸清光<br />\n唔鋸即時銀行入3萬去馬會戶口玩結果又係連輸清光<br />\n即七月前後輸了7萬幾，就算只計本金都輸了5萬，唉<br />\n係到再次勸勉各位，賭錢始終唔係正職，唔好下下就玩大注幾千過萬聲<br />\n始終返工先係真正搵到錢，賭博真係未必可以<br />\n最後想講就係如果賭博賺到錢，最好都係由馬會戶口過番銀行<br />\n沉迷賭博，倒錢落海，各位記住，控制注碼<br />\n謝謝"},{"pid":"535dc894c451800cc0a27bafa1d1d172f6d6d179","tid":2128270,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:00:55.000Z","msg":"轉頭又咪買利記<br />\n上一頁"},{"pid":"c92c30a3e8bc5335e8172c1fc208c50ffbfd52d6","tid":2128270,"uid":215570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:01:10.000Z","msg":"今晚買咩"},{"pid":"5557ade80d313a7d2ab8c8abf1112da866e1a736","tid":2128270,"uid":138267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:01:18.000Z","msg":"支持手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"},{"pid":"740afbe2e0c517320a4015e41a9e5b7d189d0663","tid":2128270,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c92c30a3e8bc5335e8172c1fc208c50ffbfd52d6","tid":2128270,"uid":215570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:01:10.000Z","msg":"今晚買咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51feec51cc3cff03a17643fcafd652c336a4f99f","tid":2128270,"uid":168857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:03:05.000Z","msg":"呢個真"},{"pid":"006a60b8da519b8de6aaace2e36e8183d3a7f476","tid":2128270,"uid":102938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:07:35.000Z","msg":"賭波都玩了好幾年起<br />\n其實每次都係咁<br />\n幾十幾百慢慢賭磨上去真係長賺多<br />\n但當你去到幾千過萬後又愈買愈大<br />\n結果就連輸幾場又係輸清光再入本金再繼續輸多<br />\n就算強如巴塞（我最鍾意美斯）都會輸比中下游<br />\n所以唔好以為巴塞讓球盤可能連續456場都大炒人贏<br />\n但運氣一唔好可能連輸番234場<br />\n所以賭博注碼真係唔好下下用到幾千以上玩"},{"pid":"6ec8a884b066930f55a4e8a585c496129099a98d","tid":2128270,"uid":324930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:08:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ff2ae894dd8f66a5047ea2cf3ebb6785d55aae2","tid":2128270,"uid":165482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有賭未為輸<br />\n今晚再黎過"},{"pid":"d2da411a4d202c268b4ebc377d4f126dd2e00beb","tid":2128270,"uid":102938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:11:02.000Z","msg":"係到在此感謝各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好有正能量互相勸勉鼓勵加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1637e5b6fb966bf88c743593f35640cf107089ef","tid":2128270,"uid":35852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:11:03.000Z","msg":"set 過止賺位lo